        <title type="html"><![CDATA[界面配置]]></title>
        <id>https://kinseyy.github.io/posts/theme/step-2</id>
        <link href="https://kinseyy.github.io/posts/theme/step-2"/>
        <updated>2022-08-03T16:30:00.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2>文章分类</h2>
<p>分类用于归类系列文章。</p>
<ul>
<li>一级分类</li>
</ul>
<pre><code class="language-md">---
title: 标题
categories: Valaxy Theme Hairy
---
</code></pre>
<ul>
<li>多级分类</li>
</ul>
<pre><code class="language-md">---
title: 标题
categories:
  - aaa
  - bbb
  - ccc
---
</code></pre>
<br/><p>访问 <a href="" target="_blank"></a> 阅读全文。</p>]]></content>
